<lb ed="T" n="0769a13"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0769a14"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0769a15"/><cb:docNumber>No. 500</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="T" n="0769a16"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note type="orig" place="foot text" n="0769002" resp="Taisho">（佛說）＋羅【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769002">羅【大】，佛說羅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769002"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">佛說羅</rdg></app>云忍辱經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0769a17" ed="T"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0769a18"/>
<lb n="0769a19" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">西晉沙門<note place="foot text" n="0769003" type="orig" resp="Taisho">（釋）＋法炬【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0769003" resp="CBETA">法炬【大】，釋法炬【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769003"><lem wit="【大】">法炬</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">釋法炬</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0769a20" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT14p0769a2001">阿難曰：「吾從佛聞如是。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0769a2010" rend="inline">一時，佛在舍衛國祇
<lb ed="T" n="0769a21"/>樹給孤獨園，時<note resp="Taisho" n="0769004" place="foot text" type="orig">鶖露＝秋露【宋】【宮】＊，鶖鷺【元】【明】＊</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769004">鶖露【大】＊，秋露【宋】【宮】＊，鶖鷺【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0769004"><lem wit="【大】">鶖露</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">秋露</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">鶖鷺</rdg></app>子與羅云俱以平旦
<lb n="0769a22" ed="T"/>著衣法服、執持應器，入城求食。時<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0769005">〔有〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0769005" resp="CBETA">有【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769005"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>輕薄
<lb ed="T" n="0769a23"/>者，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0769006" type="orig">逢＝遙【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769006" type="mod" resp="CBETA">逢【大】，遙【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769006"><lem wit="【大】">逢</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">遙</rdg></app>見兩賢，意念曰：「瞿曇沙門第一弟子
<lb n="0769a24" ed="T"/>與羅云分<note n="0769007" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">衛＝請【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0769007" type="mod">衛【大】，請【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769007"><lem wit="【大】">衛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">請</rdg></app>。」即興毒意，取地沙土，著<app type="star" corresp="#0769004"><lem wit="【大】">鶖
<lb n="0769a25" ed="T"/>露</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">秋露</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">鶖鷺</rdg></app>子鉢中、擊羅云首。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0769a2509">師見羅云血流污面，
<lb ed="T" n="0769a26"/>師曰：「為<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0769008">〔佛〕－【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769008">佛【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0769008"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>弟子，慎無含毒，當以慈心愍傷
<lb ed="T" n="0769a27"/>眾生。世尊常云：『忍者最快，唯慧者能。』<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0769009">吾聞佛戒＝聞佛說誡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769009" type="mod" resp="CBETA">吾聞佛戒【大】，聞佛說誡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769009"><lem wit="【大】">吾聞
<lb n="0769a28" ed="T"/>佛戒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">聞佛說誡</rdg></app>，終身不<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="0769010" resp="Taisho">犯＝邪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769010" type="mod" resp="CBETA">犯【大】，邪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769010"><lem wit="【大】">犯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">邪</rdg></app>，吾自攝心，以忍為寶。恣
<lb ed="T" n="0769a29"/>心履惡，猶自投火，貢高自見，愚者謂健，不
<pb n="0769b" xml:id="T14.0500.0769b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0769b01" ed="T"/>計殃禍，當還害已；恣心之禍重於須<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0769011">彌＋（首戴須彌）【元】【明】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769011">彌【大】，彌首戴須彌【元】【明】</note><app n="0769011"><lem wit="【大】">彌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">彌首戴須彌</rdg></app>，畢
<lb n="0769b02" ed="T"/>已年壽以當惡罪，十六分中未<note resp="Taisho" n="0769012" place="foot text" type="orig">減＝滅【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0769012" type="mod">減【大】，滅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769012"><lem wit="【大】">減</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">滅</rdg></app>其一。愚
<lb ed="T" n="0769b03"/>人作行惡<note n="0769013" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔向〕－【宋】【宮】</note><note n="0769013" type="mod" resp="CBETA">向【大】，〔－〕【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0769013"><lem wit="【大】">向</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>清淨持戒沙門，猶若逆風把
<lb n="0769b04" ed="T"/>炬火行，狂愚不捨，必自燒身；弊人懷毒，自
<lb n="0769b05" ed="T"/>以為慧。如比丘<note resp="Taisho" n="0769014" place="foot text" type="orig">怙＝怗【宋】，沾【元】【明】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0769014" resp="CBETA">怙【大】，怗【宋】，沾【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769014"><lem wit="【大】">怙</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">怗</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">沾</rdg></app>沙門四道，為佛弟子，常
<lb ed="T" n="0769b06"/>當伏心，惡<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0769015" resp="Taisho">生＝至【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0769015" type="mod">生【大】，至【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769015"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">至</rdg></app>即滅，勇中之上。天神帝王，雖
<lb n="0769b07" ed="T"/>謂多力，不如忍惡，其力無上。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0769b0712" rend="inline">羅云見血流
<lb n="0769b08" ed="T"/>下交面，臨水澡血而自說曰：「我痛斯須，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0769016" type="orig">奈＝念【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769016" type="mod" resp="CBETA">奈【大】，念【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769016"><lem wit="【大】">奈</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">念</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0769b09"/>彼長苦！斯人惡<note resp="Taisho" n="0769017" place="foot text" type="orig">〔也〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769017">也【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0769017"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，斯地亦惡。<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0769018">余＝奈【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769018" type="mod" resp="CBETA">余【大】，奈【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769018"><lem wit="【大】">余</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">奈</rdg></app>無慍心，悲
<lb ed="T" n="0769b10"/>奈彼何？佛是吾尊，教吾大慈。狂悖之人，志
<lb ed="T" n="0769b11"/>趣凶虐，沙門默忍，以成高德。凶者狼<note n="0769019" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">殘＝滅【宋】</note><note n="0769019" type="mod" resp="CBETA">殘【大】，滅【宋】</note><app n="0769019"><lem wit="【大】">殘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">滅</rdg></app>，愚
<lb ed="T" n="0769b12"/>人敬焉；沙門守忍，狂愚是輕。斯人惡<app type="star" corresp="#0769017"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，我
<lb ed="T" n="0769b13"/>焉能<note n="0769020" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">惡歟＝慈餘【宋】【宮】，慈濟【元】【明】</note><note type="mod" n="0769020" resp="CBETA">惡歟【大】，慈餘【宋】【宮】，慈濟【元】【明】</note><app n="0769020"><lem wit="【大】">惡歟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">慈餘</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">慈濟</rdg></app>？輪轉無際，豈一<note resp="Taisho" n="0769021" place="foot text" type="orig">向＝面【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0769021" type="mod">向【大】，面【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769021"><lem wit="【大】">向</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">面</rdg></app>乎？吾欲以
<lb n="0769b14" ed="T"/>佛至真之經喻誨愚惑，猶以<note resp="Taisho" n="0769022" place="foot text" type="orig">〔利〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0769022" resp="CBETA">利【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769022"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>劍<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0769023">割＝害【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769023">割【大】，害【宮】</note><app n="0769023"><lem wit="【大】">割</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">害</rdg></app>彼臭
<lb n="0769b15" ed="T"/>屍，屍不知痛，非劍之不利，乃死屍之無知。
<lb ed="T" n="0769b16"/>以天甘露食彼溷猪，猪捨之走，非甘露之
<lb n="0769b17" ed="T"/>不美，乃臭蟲之所不珍矣。以佛真言，訓世
<lb n="0769b18" ed="T"/><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0769024">凶＝嬰【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0769024" resp="CBETA">凶【大】，嬰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769024"><lem wit="【大】">凶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">嬰</rdg></app>愚，不亦然乎。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0769b1807" rend="inline">師徒俱還。飯竟澡<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0769025" type="orig">鉢＝浴【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769025">鉢【大】，浴【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769025"><lem wit="【大】">鉢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">浴</rdg></app>，洗
<lb n="0769b19" ed="T"/>手漱口，俱到佛所，稽首佛足。<app corresp="#0769004" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">鶖露</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">秋露</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">鶖鷺</rdg></app>子退坐，
<lb n="0769b20" ed="T"/>具以本末向佛陳之。世尊告曰：「夫惡<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0769026" type="orig">〔心〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769026" type="mod" resp="CBETA">心【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769026"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>之
<lb n="0769b21" ed="T"/>興，興<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0769027" type="orig">己＝已【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0769027" type="mod">己【大】，已【宮】</note><app n="0769027"><lem wit="【大】">己</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">已</rdg></app>之衰。輕薄者命終至于夜半，當入
<lb n="0769b22" ed="T"/>無擇地獄之中。獄鬼加痛，毒無不至，八萬四
<lb ed="T" n="0769b23"/>千歲，其壽乃終。魂神更受含毒<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0769028">蟒＝蝮【宋】，蛟【元】【明】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0769028" type="mod">蟒【大】，蝮【宋】，蛟【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769028"><lem wit="【大】">蟒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">蝮</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【宮】">蛟</rdg></app>身，毒重
<lb ed="T" n="0769b24"/>還害其身。終而復始，續受<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0769029" resp="Taisho">蝮＝蟒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769029" type="mod" resp="CBETA">蝮【大】，蟒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769029"><lem wit="【大】">蝮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">蟒</rdg></app>形，常食<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0769030">沙＝地【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769030">沙【大】，地【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769030"><lem wit="【大】">沙</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">地</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0769b25"/>土，萬歲乃畢。以瞋恚意向持戒人，故受毒
<lb n="0769b26" ed="T"/>身；以沙土投鉢中，故世世食沙土而死。罪
<lb ed="T" n="0769b27"/>畢乃出，得生為人。母懷之時，常有重病，家
<lb n="0769b28" ed="T"/>中日耗，生兒頑鈍，都無手足。其親驚<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0769031" type="orig">怪＝怖【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769031" type="mod" resp="CBETA">怪【大】，怖【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769031"><lem wit="【大】">怪</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">怖</rdg></app>，宗
<lb ed="T" n="0769b29"/>家皆然，曰：『斯何<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0769032" type="orig">妖＋（怪）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0769032" type="mod">妖【大】，妖怪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769032"><lem wit="【大】">妖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">妖怪</rdg></app>？<note resp="Taisho" n="0769033" place="foot text" type="orig">來＝當【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769033" type="mod" resp="CBETA">來【大】，當【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769033"><lem wit="【大】">來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">當</rdg></app>為不祥。』即取捐之，
<pb ed="T" xml:id="T14.0500.0769c" n="0769c"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0769c01"/>著于四衢。路人往來無不<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0769034">愕＝釋【宋】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769034">愕【大】，釋【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0769034"><lem wit="【大】">愕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">釋</rdg></app>然，<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0769035">〔或以瓦石擲〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0769035" type="mod">或以瓦石擲【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769035"><lem wit="【大】">或以瓦石
<lb n="0769c02" ed="T"/>擲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，或以刀杖，皆擊其頭，<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0769036" resp="Taisho">蹈＝陷【元】【明】</note><note type="mod" n="0769036" resp="CBETA">蹈【大】，陷【元】【明】</note><app n="0769036"><lem wit="【大】">蹈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">陷</rdg></app>腦窮苦，旬月
<lb ed="T" n="0769c03"/>乃死。死後魂神即復更生，輒無手足，<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0769037">頑鈍＝殘頑【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769037">頑鈍【大】，殘頑【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769037"><lem wit="【大】">頑鈍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">殘頑</rdg></app>
<lb n="0769c04" ed="T"/>如前，<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0769038" resp="Taisho">經＝連【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0769038" resp="CBETA">經【大】，連【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769038"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">連</rdg></app>五百世，重罪乃畢。後乃為人，常有
<lb ed="T" n="0769c05"/>頭痛之患。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0769c0505">世尊重曰：「<app type="star" corresp="#0769004"><lem wit="【大】">鶖露</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">秋露</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">鶖鷺</rdg></app>子！夫人處世不
<lb ed="T" n="0769c06"/><note n="0769039" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">惟＝唯【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0769039" resp="CBETA">惟【大】，唯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769039"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">唯</rdg></app>忍者，所生之處，不值佛世、違法遠僧，常
<lb n="0769c07" ed="T"/>在三<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0769040">塗＝途【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769040">塗【大】，途【宮】</note><app n="0769040"><lem wit="【大】">塗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">途</rdg></app>，終而復始，輒有劫數。若蒙餘福得
<lb n="0769c08" ed="T"/>出為人，稟操常愚、𣧑虐自隨，乃心嫉聖、謗
<lb n="0769c09" ed="T"/>毀至尊，為人醜陋，眾所惡憎，生輒貧窮，<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0769041">仕＝士【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769041">仕【大】，士【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769041"><lem wit="【大】">仕</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">士</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0769c10"/>不得官，願與<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0769042" resp="Taisho">意＝福【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769042">意【大】，福【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769042"><lem wit="【大】">意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">福</rdg></app>違，天神聖賢所不祐助，夜
<lb n="0769c11" ed="T"/>常惡夢，妖怪首尾，飛禍縱橫，所處不寧，心
<lb ed="T" n="0769c12"/>常恐怖。斯之所由，由不忍伏<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0769043" type="orig">〔惡心〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769043" type="mod" resp="CBETA">惡心【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769043"><lem wit="【大】">惡心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，故使然
<lb ed="T" n="0769c13"/>耳。忍惡行者，所生常安，眾禍消滅，願輒如
<lb n="0769c14" ed="T"/>志，顏貌煒曄，身強少病，財<note n="0769044" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">榮尊貴＝福榮尊【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0769044" type="mod">榮尊貴【大】，福榮尊【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769044"><lem wit="【大】">榮尊貴</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">福榮尊</rdg></app>，皆由忍
<lb ed="T" n="0769c15"/>辱、慈<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0769045">惠＝慧【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769045">惠【大】，慧【宮】</note><app n="0769045"><lem wit="【大】">惠</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">慧</rdg></app>濟眾之所致也。忍<note resp="Taisho" n="0769046" place="foot text" type="orig">之＝便【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769046">之【大】，便【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769046"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">便</rdg></app>為福，身安親
<lb ed="T" n="0769c16"/>寧，宗家<note place="foot text" n="0769047" type="orig" resp="Taisho">和興＝餘慶【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0769047" resp="CBETA">和興【大】，餘慶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769047"><lem wit="【大】">和興</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">餘慶</rdg></app>，未嘗不歡。智者深見，<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="0769048" resp="Taisho">迮＝敬【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769048">迮【大】，敬【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769048"><lem wit="【大】">迮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">敬</rdg></app><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0769049">伏＋（安親寧宗）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0769049" type="mod">伏【大】，伏安親寧宗【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769049"><lem wit="【大】">伏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">伏安親寧宗</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0769c17"/>其心。<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0769050">心＝惡【明】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769050">心【大】，惡【明】</note><app n="0769050"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">惡</rdg></app>者誤人，破家危身，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0769051" type="orig">王法＝為王【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0769051" type="mod">王法【大】，為王【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769051"><lem wit="【大】">王法</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">為王</rdg></app>所戮，地獄
<lb n="0769c18" ed="T"/>燒煮，或為餓鬼，亦為畜生，皆心之過也。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0769c1816">世
<lb n="0769c19" ed="T"/>尊又曰：「寧<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0769052" type="orig">以＝臥【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0769052">以【大】，臥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769052"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">臥</rdg></app>利劍貫腹截肌，自投火中；慎
<lb ed="T" n="0769c20"/>無履惡。寧戴須彌，<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0769053" resp="Taisho">迮＝奪【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0769053" resp="CBETA">迮【大】，奪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769053"><lem wit="【大】">迮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">奪</rdg></app>毀其命，投于巨海，魚
<lb n="0769c21" ed="T"/>鱉所吞；慎無為惡矣。不知其義，慎無妄言。
<lb n="0769c22" ed="T"/>佛之明法，與俗相背，俗之所珍，道<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0769054" resp="Taisho">之＝大【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769054" type="mod" resp="CBETA">之【大】，大【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769054"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">大</rdg></app>所賤。
<lb ed="T" n="0769c23"/>清濁異流，明愚異趣，忠侫相讐，邪常嫉正。
<pb ed="T" xml:id="T14.0500.0770a" n="0770a"/>
<lb n="0770a01" ed="T"/>故<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0770001">嗜＝著【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0770001" resp="CBETA">嗜【大】，著【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770001"><lem wit="【大】">嗜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">著</rdg></app>欲之人，不好我無慾之行也。寧<note place="foot text" n="0770002" type="orig" resp="Taisho">吞＝嗒【宮】</note><note n="0770002" type="mod" resp="CBETA">吞【大】，嗒【宮】</note><app n="0770002"><lem wit="【大】">吞</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">嗒</rdg></app>然
<lb n="0770a02" ed="T"/>炭，無謗三尊。忍之為明，踰於日月。龍象之
<lb n="0770a03" ed="T"/>力，可謂盛猛，比之於忍，萬萬不如一。七寶
<lb ed="T" n="0770a04"/>之<note place="foot text" n="0770003" type="orig" resp="Taisho">燿＝嚮【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0770003" resp="CBETA">燿【大】，嚮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770003"><lem wit="【大】">燿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">嚮</rdg></app>，凡俗所貴，然其招憂，以致災患；忍之
<lb ed="T" n="0770a05"/>為寶，終始獲安。布施十方，雖有大福，福不
<lb ed="T" n="0770a06"/>如<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0770004">忍＝也【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0770004" resp="CBETA">忍【大】，也【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770004"><lem wit="【大】">忍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">也</rdg></app>。懷忍行<note n="0770005" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">慈＝慧【宋】【元】【宮】，惠【明】</note><note type="mod" n="0770005" resp="CBETA">慈【大】，慧【宋】【元】【宮】，惠【明】</note><app n="0770005"><lem wit="【大】">慈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">慧</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">惠</rdg></app>，世世無怨，中心恬然，<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0770006" resp="Taisho">終＝眾【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0770006" type="mod">終【大】，眾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770006"><lem wit="【大】">終</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">眾</rdg></app>
<lb n="0770a07" ed="T"/>無毒害。世無所怙，唯忍可恃。忍為安宅，災
<lb n="0770a08" ed="T"/>怪不生；忍為神鎧，眾兵不加；忍為大<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0770007">舟＝身【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0770007">舟【大】，身【宮】</note><app n="0770007"><lem wit="【大】">舟</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">身</rdg></app>，可
<lb ed="T" n="0770a09"/>以渡難；忍為良藥，能濟眾命。忍者之志，何
<lb ed="T" n="0770a10"/>願不獲？若欲願為飛行皇帝，典四天下、第二
<lb ed="T" n="0770a11"/><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0770008">天＋（天）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770008" type="mod" resp="CBETA">天【大】，天天【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770008"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">天天</rdg></app>帝釋及上第六天，壽命無極，身體香潔，
<lb n="0770a12" ed="T"/>所願自然，猶若家物，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0770009">取之＝所之【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0770009">取之【大】，所之【宮】</note><app n="0770009"><lem wit="【大】">取之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">所之</rdg></app>即得；志願清淨
<lb ed="T" n="0770a13"/>沙門四道，求之可得，在己所向。吾今得佛，諸
<lb ed="T" n="0770a14"/>天所宗，獨步三界，忍力所致。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0770a1412" rend="inline">佛告諸沙門：「當
<lb n="0770a15" ed="T"/>誦《忍經》，無忘須臾，懷之、識之、誦之、宣之。當宣
<lb n="0770a16" ed="T"/>忍德，以濟眾生。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0770a1607">佛說經竟，諸沙門皆大歡喜，
<lb ed="T" n="0770a17"/>作禮而去。</p></cb:div>
